<title>USA: Computervision names William Wilson CFO.</title>
<headline>Computervision names William Wilson CFO.</headline>
<dateline>BEDFORD, Mass. 1997-06-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>ComputerVision Corp said Thursday William Wilson has been appointed senior vice president and chief financial officer.</p>
<p>The company said Wilson replaces William Foniri, who will serve as the chief financial officer for CV Services International when the sale of that business to M.D. Sass is completed.</p>
<p>The company said Wilson will be responsible for the finance and administration function at the company.</p>
<p>Wilson comes from Arch Communications Group Inc, where he was executive vice president and chief financial officer, the company said.</p>
